{"tid":1592462,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"慢慢香港同中共做既野一樣","createTime":"2019-09-24T15:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T17:17:20.000Z","uid":37038,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a1112af7d11511e4ca08a753cc97ca26586c5285","tid":1592462,"uid":37038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:29:21.000Z","msg":"有時好多野<br />\n有因必有果<br />\n<br />\n中共做既野係因<br />\n換成香港咁既局面係果<br />\n<br />\n香港抗爭失理智係因<br />\n助長中共惡行係果<br />\n<br />\n當你唔理任何法治<br />\n唔相信法律<br />\n就同中共核心既理念一模一樣<br />\n<br />\n曾幾何時中國出左一個左右局勢既抗爭者<br />\n佢年青又勇武<br />\n理念極高尚行動力又快<br />\n佢叫毛澤東<br />\n<br />\n香港抗爭同毛澤東既理念愈行愈近<br />\n靠既係指鹿為馬<br />\n靠既係激昂情緒<br />\n靠既係草根起義"},{"pid":"9d33b9147ddd2d959c0bbf8d1678fa08b81c16a5","tid":1592462,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"776c4b880d3449bc34efe5e846ed07398374c846","tid":1592462,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:31:40.000Z","msg":"［請幫推行動post］今星期四：和你塞 美心MX<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590453</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4KHbAX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4KHbAX.jpg&h=3211b048&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2b3ff96f86eb41bf64ee73209f3a07773681113","tid":1592462,"uid":37038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:18:32.000Z","msg":"因果循環<br />\n生生不息"},{"pid":"c51e764faa2202caf7840bc39aab91c8cbdd2993","tid":1592462,"uid":37038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T16:19:48.000Z","msg":"物極必反<br />\n否極泰來"},{"pid":"114616ae6d45d87b8644d0de38